Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有犹豫 没有等待 我就是脑子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't hesitate, I don't wait, I just, in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻想到凯特・莫斯和楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}instantly think of Kate Moss and the stairs.
