Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德在她本人的证词中 提到凯特・莫斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard, in her direct testimony, mentioned Kate Moss.
