Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,审判法里有个概念叫“开门”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a concept in trial law called "opening the door."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如“也许我们都同意 有些东西是不相关的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like, "Maybe there's something we both agree is irrelevant."
