Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“这对我的案子有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But, on my side of things, it would help me and help my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为法官裁定存在偏见 所以我不能提”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I know I can't bring it up, because the judge says it's irrelevant, or it's too prejudicial, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯特・莫斯和楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kate Moss and the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是约翰尼・德普先注意到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp picked up on it first, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他笑得好像“真不敢相信她这么说”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He smiled like, "I can't believe she just said that,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这打开了门 凯特・莫斯不打算作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because it opened the door. Kate Moss was not going to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个关键时刻 因为它使得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was a real pivotal moment because this allowed
