Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为他会把你妹妹扔下楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You thought he was gonna throw your sister down the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他把凯特・莫斯 扔下楼梯一样 是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like he had thrown Kate Moss down the stairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对着惠特尼挥拳了 而且我听过传闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He swung at Whitney, and I'd heard a rumor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事的一个模糊的传闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a vague rumor, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so it's what I thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果凯特・莫斯过来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Kate Moss were to come in and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“约翰尼从来没有 对我有过肢体或任何暴力”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"No, Johnny was never physically abusive or anything to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这对安柏的说辞 会有毁灭性的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then that would be a really big, detrimental thing to Amber's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪审员们被告知 “评估可信度是你们的职责”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jurors are told, "It's your job to evaluate credibility."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你发现一个人在一件事上撒了谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, you know, if you find someone is lying on one issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以判断他们是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you can conclude they're liars in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道约翰尼的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know the truth about Johnny.
