Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒体界的很多人 在他们还在约会的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of people in the media, back then when they were dating,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将之视为一种不稳定的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was looked at as somewhat of a volatile relationship.
