Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（演员破坏酒店后获释）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信公平和正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe in fairness and justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe in the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 女士们 先生们 请坐 下一位证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, ladies and gentlemen. Please be seated. Your next witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 法官大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生请凯特・莫斯上证人席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, Mr. Depp calls Kate Moss to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 举起你的右手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, ma'am. If you could raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否发誓或确认 在法律的惩罚下说实话？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you swear or affirm to tell the truth under penalty of law?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I do. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问莫斯小姐 你和德普先生的 感情关系持续了多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For how long, Ms. Moss, were you and Mr. Depp a romantic couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1994年到1998年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ninety-four to 1998.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和德普先生 如果有的话 在牙买加时发生了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What, if anything, happened when you were in Jamaica with Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们准备离开房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We were leaving the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我离开房间时 我滑下了楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, as I left the room, I slid down the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄伤了我的背\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I hurt my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生有没有把你推下楼？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Mr. Depp push you in any way down the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你们交往的过程中 他有没有把你推下楼过？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}During the course of your relationship, did he ever push you down any stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 他从没推过我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, he never pushed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踢我 或者把我扔下过任何楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}kicked me, or threw me... ...down any stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莫斯小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, Ms. Moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些陪审员应该听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These jurors are supposed to be listening
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭上的每一个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to every single word of everything that's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于 他们可能会停止听你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The problem is they might stop listening to you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为在那个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because, at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不再觉得你是可信的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they no longer find you credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刻对安柏・赫德极其不利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That moment was very damaging for Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道陪审团在想什么 但如果这是一场可信度的游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't know what the jury is thinking, but if it's a credibility game,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}which it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他们可能已经 不会再听她的任何陈述了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they may have tuned out to the rest of her case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…用另一只手猛击她的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...whacking her repeatedly in the face with the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…就因为那一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...because of that very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子的依据是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This... This case rests on the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那篇文章的第一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The first sentence of that... of that article.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 -“我变成了家庭暴力的代言人”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - "I was...I was... I became the face of domestic violence."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子其实是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the case really is, the lawyers' case is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们要证明你说的一切都是假的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We are gonna prove that everything you said is not true."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（布莱恩・卡伦 喜剧演员和演员 PBD播客嘉宾）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（为挑战赫德 关于虐待的指控 德普的律师）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你的下一位证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, your next witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“这是你编的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You're making this stuff up."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出你的全名以供记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could you state your full name for the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-香农・库里 -你的职业是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Shannon Curry. - What do you do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名临床和法证心理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am a clinical and forensic psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么参与到这起案子的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How'd you get involved in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生的律师请我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was asked, uh, by counsel for Mr. Depp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来对赫德小姐进行心理评估\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to provide a psychological evaluation of Ms. Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有被要求 对德普先生做心理评估？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Were you ever asked to do a psychological evaluation of Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在审理期间 双方都将心理健康和药物成瘾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}During the trial, both sides have been using mental health and substance addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为对付另一方的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as weapons against the other team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常情况下 提起诉讼的一方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what usually happens is the people bringing the case
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会有一名心理健康专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}usually have a mental health expert
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诊断对方患有严重精神健康障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}diagnosing the opposing person with a bad mental health disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德小姐的评估支持两种诊断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The results of Ms. Heard's evaluation supported two diagnoses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即边缘型人格障碍和组织型人格障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}borderline personality disorder and histrionic personality disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后为自己的辩护的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then the person defending themselves in the trial will typically try to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常会说：“我没有那么糟糕的诊断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"No, no, no, I don't have that bad diagnosis."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有能让陪审团和观众 更加同情的病症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I have something that evokes more pity from a jury and an audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如创伤后应激障碍”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}something like PTSD."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和赫德小姐总共会见了约29小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so I met with Ms. Heard, um, for a total of about 29 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要意见是赫德小姐 对亲密伴侣的暴力行为的报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The main opinion is that Ms. Heard's report of intimate partner violence
