Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我没有印象 -这个也没有印象？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I don't recall that. - You don't recall that either?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和德普先生一起下的飞机吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you leave the plane with Mr. Depp?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了自己的家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I went to my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 德普先生当时状态如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, and what was Mr. Depp's state?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得他当时是否昏倒了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't recall if he was passed out or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天坐在这里 宣过誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As you're sitting here today, under oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不记得德普先生有没有晕倒？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you honestly can't remember if Mr. Depp was passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生是有可能 在飞机上踢安柏的 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Mr. Depp could have kicked Amber on that plane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not that I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下飞机时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you got off the plane from Boston, you knew Ms. Heard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道赫德小姐在生你的气 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was angry with you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她总是很生气 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was always angry, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问了杜特斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you asked Mr. Deuters... He was your personal assist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的私人助理 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Deuters was your personal assistant, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜特斯先生是其中之一 是的 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, Mr. Deuters was one of them, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一次请杜特斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, and it wasn't uncommon for you to ask Mr. Deuters
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表你跟赫德小姐沟通 是吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to communicate with Ms. Heard on your behalf, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的所有私人助理都代表我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It wasn't uncommon for any of them to communicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟赫德小姐沟通过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uh, with Ms. Heard on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜特斯没有作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deuters never testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普第二次站上证人席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So with Depp on the witness stand for the second time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在赫德的辩护律师试图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}here's what happened when Amber Heard's defense attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将德普助理发的短信 给陪审团看时 发生了这样的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tried to show texts from Depp's assistant to the jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能请拿出229号证物吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you pull up Exhibit 229, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据德普先生的证词 我提请采纳229号证物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Based on Mr. Depp's testimony, I'd ask to move for the admission of Exhibit 229.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-法官大人 我们能上前吗？ -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Honor...can we please approach? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（赫德的律师请求来自）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（阿兹卡瑞特法官的许可 以提交额外证据）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（社交媒体评论员 密切关注这一决定）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊天室有人说 如果我们看到杜特斯的短信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some people are saying in the chat that Deuters' texts, if that's what we're about to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会对德普不利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they're... they're not gonna look good for Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英国的审判里也出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Came up in the UK trial as well. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关踢安柏的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About ki... Uh, something about kicking Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（陪审团没有看到短信）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（阿兹卡瑞特法官没有允许采纳）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们没能让杜特斯的短信被采纳 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- They didn't get that Deuters stuff in. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟法官磋商后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After that sidebar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本・罗腾伯恩律师放弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}attorney Ben Rottenborn moves on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些短信没有成为证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and those texts stay out of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子里有太多证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, there was so much evidence in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在预审听证会上 他们必须裁定哪些是可接受的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the pre-trial hearings, they have to, you know, rule what is admissible,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪些不是 所以当进入庭审时 可以加快进度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what isn't, just so that when we get to trial, we can, you know, speed things along,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下庭审的关键证据 以供陪审员下定决心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}only have what's, you know, essential for the trial, for the jurors to make up their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会想要排除证据？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would you want to exclude evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它会伤害你 这就是原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because it hurts you. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普是一位大师级演员 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depp is a master actor, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他几乎不用动就能引诱我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He seduced all of us by barely moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要把艺术和人品分开 取决于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's your decision whether you want to separate the art from the artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（马特沃顿 演员 PBD播客嘉宾）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普是很棒的演员 但我也觉得他是热爱暴力的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think Johnny Depp is a terrific actor. I also happen to think he's a violent lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了这些可怕的指控之外 他还是很讨人喜欢的 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a likeable guy, other than these horrific allegations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜欢 他在《加勒比海盗》里的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody loved him in The Pirates of the Caribbean,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是带着一些光环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there's a little bit of what's called a halo effect around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（安柏赫德的律师团队 转变了提问思路）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（转而质疑约翰尼德普的人品）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这些照片、短信和证词 是具有毁灭性的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that's why these photos, the texts, the testimony, is so devastating,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这会打破我们对德普先生的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because it shatters that perception we have of Mr. Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗贝坦尼 是跟你一起嗑药的好朋友 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Paul Bettany's a good friend that you've done drugs with, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个奇怪的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a strange question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗贝塔尼是我的好朋友 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, Paul Bettany's a good friend. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们当时都非常喜欢 使用管制药物和酒精\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The two of you shared an enjoyment of controlled drugs and alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是或不是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at that time, yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你和他一起吸过毒？ -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You've done drugs with him? - Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可卡因 对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cocaine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可卡因 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, cocaine, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒精\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒精 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alcohol, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你在试着 表现得像个绅士了 是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now you try to conduct yourself as a gentleman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生 这是你和保罗・贝坦尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Depp, this is a text message exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在2013年6月11日的往来短信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that you had with Paul Bettany on June 11th, 2013.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你发短信给贝塔尼先生 “我们烧了安柏吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You text Mr. Bettany, "Let's burn Amber."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你看到了吗？ -我看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You see that? - I do see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一条短信 你说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The next text down, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们先把她淹死 然后烧了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会操她烧焦的尸体 以确保她死透了”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没读错吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did I read that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全没读错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You certainly did, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你写的是之后成为了你妻子的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you wrote that about the woman who would later become your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色幽默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dark humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些短信…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The text messages that... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉每个人都要经历这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I apologize that everyone's had to, uh, experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为提到的一些内容感到羞耻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am ashamed of, uh...of some of the references, uh, made.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我羞耻的是 当时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm, uh, embarrassed that, at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个激动的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the heat of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时感觉到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the heat of the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, that I was feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我变得黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, went to...went to dark places.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 大家请坐 结案陈词 罗腾伯恩先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, you may be seated. All right, closing arguments. Mr. Rottenborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢 -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thanks. - Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想德普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think about the message
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他的律师们试图对安柏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that Mr. Depp and his attorneys are sending to Amber,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及每一位家暴受害者传达的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and by extension, to every victim of domestic abuse everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当德普先生提起这场诽谤诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When Mr. Depp brought this case for defamation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德女士全力以赴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ms. Heard went all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她编出了一个令人震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She spun a story of shocking,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人难以承受的残忍虐待故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}overwhelming, brutal abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没有拍照 就没发生过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"If you didn't take pictures, it didn't happen."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你拍了照 那就是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"If you did take pictures, they're fake."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她来到这间法庭 准备给出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She came into this courtroom prepared to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生中最棒的表演 她也做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}give the performance of her life, and she gave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有寻求医治 你没受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You didn't seek medical treatment, you weren't injured."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的去找过医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"If you did seek medical treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're crazy."
