Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.56,0:30:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Answer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.92,0:30:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah!
