Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.12,0:30:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Answer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都回答都是“是的”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All yesses. 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:30:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow.
