Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.60,0:31:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千万美元！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ten million dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.80,0:31:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们陪审团裁定 判处五百万美元的惩罚性赔偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We the jury award punitive damages in the amount of five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh! - Yes!
