Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.24,0:31:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是否认为 赫德小姐证明了诽谤的全部要素？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you find that Ms. Heard has proven all the elements of defamation?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.88,0:31:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Answer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.04,0:31:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于约翰C德普二世\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As against John C. Depp II,
