Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.88,0:31:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们 先生们 你们在本案中的工作到此结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, this concludes your service on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.80,0:31:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要再次感谢你们 在这次审判中的奉献和辛勤工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanna thank you again for your dedication and your hard work during this trial, 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这句话代表了这里的每一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I know I speak for everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.92,0:31:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny! Johnny! Johnny! Johnny! Johnny! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.92,0:31:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普和安柏・赫德的 诽谤案宣读了判决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp and Amber Heard defamation trial announced its verdict,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.72,0:32:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,判决约翰尼・德普胜诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}ruling in favor of Johnny Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.64,0:32:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你 约翰尼！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Love you, Johnny! We love you, Johnny! We lo...
