Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼 我爱你 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oi, John, Johnny, Johnny, Johnny, I love you, bro. I love you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.20,0:32:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一场如此残酷的战役 却没有获得太多胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A verdict with little victory when the battle has been so brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.08,0:32:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏・赫德不是一个好证人 陪审团对此给出了反馈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard was not a good witness, and juries react to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.56,0:32:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得陪审团弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think the jury got it wrong, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对陪审团的判决非常失望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm very disappointed in the jury verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.80,0:32:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是强权男人的 又一次巨大胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think this is another big win for powerful men,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.00,0:32:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对女人来说是巨大的失败\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it's a colossal loss for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.40,0:32:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在判决之后）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.96,0:32:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（社交媒体上有部分人 为安柏・赫德激情发声）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.76,0:32:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（但大部分人在庆祝）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.04,0:32:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种羞辱性的仪式 意在让女人认清自己的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was a humiliation ritual intending to put women in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.24,0:32:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说出自己遭受虐待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you speak out about abuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.20,0:32:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将会付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.28,0:32:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们都想要的判决 各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was the verdict we all wanted, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.44,0:32:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普 德普 德普！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny Depp, Depp, Depp! Johnny Depp, Depp, Depp!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.00,0:32:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（约翰尼・德普赢了）
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.40,0:33:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在德普的众多网络支持者 庆祝他的胜利的同时）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.92,0:33:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（部分新闻媒体开始提出质疑）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.80,0:33:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们羞辱赫德时获得的快感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The pleasure with which we're humiliating Amber Heard
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们对 约翰尼・德普的美化一样可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is... is just as, I... I think, troubling as... as the glamorization of... of... of Johnny Depp in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.96,0:33:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当那是一个我们认识的人 我们可能很喜欢的人时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When it's somebody that we know, somebody that we maybe like,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不愿思考\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they don't wanna have to think
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人真的可能 做出法庭上指控他的那些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this person is really capable of doing what's alleged in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.16,0:33:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到的关于这个话题的邮件 比以往任何话题的都多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never had as many emails, uh, as I've received about this very topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.80,0:33:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过被虐待过的男性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've heard from men who have been, uh, abused,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.00,0:33:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过不相信赫德的女性幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've heard from women who are survivors who don't believe Amber Heard
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.76,0:33:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说她在伤害幸存者 公众有各种各样的情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and say she's hurting, uh, survivors. So there's a lot of feelings out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.44,0:33:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（我支持安柏）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这次审判能让大家警觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But one of the things I hope that this trial raises some awareness of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家庭暴力的复杂性和性别影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is the complexity of domestic violence and some of the gendered implications of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.92,0:33:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是提到家庭暴力的男性受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}particularly when we're talking about male victims of domestic violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（判决日当天）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.80,0:33:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（一个家暴幸存者群体）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.72,0:33:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（写了一封给赫德的公开信）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.12,0:33:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这封有力的公开信 说明他们并不支持她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This powerful open letter states that they don't stand with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.12,0:34:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不接受 她是她自己所声称的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they don't accept that she is who she claimed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.36,0:34:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们不会支持你”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We will not stand with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.64,0:34:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“没有任何家庭暴力受害者 会有你那样的表现”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.84,0:34:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我们支持过你 为你哭泣过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"We supported you, we wept for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.76,0:34:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为你宣传\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we rallied behind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.28,0:34:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你背叛了我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you betrayed us all."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到你说的话 让我们中的很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感到巨大痛苦 引发不好的回忆 甚至无法忍受”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的行为影响了未来 报告遭受家庭暴力的女性们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你提醒了很多幸存者 虐待不分性别
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.08,0:34:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个说出自己遭受虐待的男人 也必须被听到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.64,0:34:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我们的运动 作为武器来对付你的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.28,0:34:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说“是你逼我这么做的”的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就知道你真正的身份了 虐待者 你的受害者是约翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.76,0:34:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.08,0:34:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常受刺激 再次体验了创伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm feeling incredibly triggered and re-traumatized
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.56,0:34:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是曾经经历过亲密关系暴力的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as someone who's experienced relationship abuse in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是代替约翰尼・德普受刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I'm not feeling triggered on behalf of Johnny Depp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.04,0:34:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所看到的现状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What we're seeing happen, stereotypes that are coming out, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.56,0:34:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刻板印象出现了 说安柏・赫德是骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}uh, that were calling A-Amber Heard a liar,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.36,0:34:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将约翰尼・德普 美化成一个了不起的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who... glorifying, uh, Johnny Depp as-as-as-as this amazing man, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是“我也是运动”开始的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}um, is the reason why Me Too started.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.48,0:35:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么 活动家们想为这一刻而战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the... It's... It's...it's why activists really wanted to fight for this movement
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.28,0:35:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及这为何如此重要 因为女人没有感觉到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and why it's so important, because women didn't feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.96,0:35:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及所有性别的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and... and, you know, survivors of all genders,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.52,0:35:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得他们可以举报 不觉得这个举动是合理的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}didn't feel like they could report, didn't feel like it was gonna be welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？ “我也是运动”到头了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does it mean for that? Are we at the end of Me Too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.88,0:35:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是逆转吗？我们现在是什么情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this a reversal? Wh... Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.16,0:35:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是对“我也是运动”的反弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it's a backlash to Me Too,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.92,0:35:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到互联网展示出的现状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and what we're seeing unfold on the Internet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.80,0:35:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在证明他们是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is that we're proving them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.24,0:35:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在说：“是的 你会被噤声 你会被羞辱”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're... We're... We're saying that, "Yes, you will be silenced, you will be humiliated."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会站边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not taking any sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.28,0:35:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来赫德的确在他们交往期间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sounds like Heard did allegedly do some malicious shit 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做过据说很糟糕的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}during the course of their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.72,0:35:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但赫德每天都在 全球范围内被疯狂攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I am feeling some kind of way about the way that Heard is being inhumanely attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.68,0:35:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也让我很不是滋味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}every day on a global scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是暴力受害者的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And here's what this means for victims of abuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.24,0:35:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出的人会越来越少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}fewer victims will come forward, 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.76,0:35:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是如果他们 在那段关系中也不完美的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}especially if they haven't been perfect during the course of their relationship with the abuser.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.40,0:35:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你因为做错了某件事 不是完美的受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if you're not the perfect victim because you did something wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你反抗了 你就是不完美的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you fought back, you're an imperfect person,
