Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.12,0:36:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问社交媒体的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me ask you about social media.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那上面的声音完全是一边倒 而且对安柏赫德的攻击非常尖锐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was incredibly lopsided and vitriolic against Amber Heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.00,0:36:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那对案件结果有影响吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think that had an effect on the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.96,0:36:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-当然 -你觉得陪审团知道吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Absolutely. - You think jurors were aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.04,0:36:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会不知道？他们每天晚上都回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How can you not? They went home every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.40,0:36:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有家人 家人会上社交媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have families, the families are on social media.
