Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.68,0:36:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得陪审员们看到了那些 有被网上的声音影响吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you believe the jurors saw any of that, were swayed by any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.72,0:36:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不认为有任何理由相信 陪审员们违背了他们的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. I don't think there's any reason to believe that the jurors violated their oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.88,0:36:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在中间有十天的休息时间 因为有一个司法会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...had a ten-day break in the middle because of the judicial conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:37:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些信息不可能对他们毫无影响 而且它们非常可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no way they couldn't have been influenced by it, and it was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.56,0:37:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无处不在 但与此同时 他们每晚都在被告诫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is everywhere, but at the same time, they were admonished every single night,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.84,0:37:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们非常尊重法庭和程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, uh, they had an... tremendous amount of respect, I think, for the court and the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.56,0:37:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们都尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they were doing the best that they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.08,0:37:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反对在法庭里架摄像机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I... I was against cameras in the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.52,0:37:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我公开反对过这种做法 因为这起案件的性质敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I went on record with that, and... and had argued against it because of the sensitive nature of this.
