Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.00,0:37:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,允许摄像机进入庭审 就是对抖音玩梗敞开了大门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By allowing cameras into the trial, you opened up the space for TikTok memes.
