Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.44,0:37:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确有针锋相对的社交媒体话题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, you did have, obviously, like, competing social media hashtags, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.56,0:37:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支持其中一方或者另一方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...in support for one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很多研究表明 约翰尼・德普的话题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there was a lot of research showing that the hashtags for Johnny Depp
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.36,0:37:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全网大规模地被创造出来 并且被大肆传播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}had been essentially created and proliferated and manipulated
