Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.84,0:37:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（迈克尔・霍布斯 记者 爸爸取消我播客嘉宾）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.60,0:37:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人说是机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People say it's bots.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.64,0:37:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场审判的错误信息 规模之大是史无前例的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The scale of, like, the misinformation about this trial is truly unprecedented.
