Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.00,0:38:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Zero content.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.72,0:38:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你开始意识到 这些可能是机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then you start to realize, like, these are probably bots.
