Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.64,0:38:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看了我们 还指了我们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Johnny just looked at us and pointed at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.72,0:39:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thank you. - Than... Well, I gotta thank you.
