Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.16,0:41:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒的片段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Twenty-second clips.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这一段话并不能代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So the transcripts of them...are not representative
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.68,0:41:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提取出那段话的两三个小时的对话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of two hours, or the three hours those clips are excerpt from.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.96,0:41:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能代表是什么意思？ 当然能代表 都录音录下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What? What do you mean, it doesn't represent it? What... What do you mean by that? Yeah, it does! 'Cause... 'Cause it's in... It's in the recording!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.24,0:41:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能坐在那里张嘴就来 “那不能代表…” 就是能代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't sit there and say, "Well, it doesn't represent the whole..." It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.48,0:41:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安柏・赫德想让 约翰尼・德普成为一个角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amber Heard wanted to characterize Johnny Depp as a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,审判产生了很多梗 现在那场访谈又有了一些梗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were many memes from the trial, but now memes from the... Now memes from the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.04,0:42:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普的律师称你的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Depp lawyer said... called your testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.36,0:42:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“人生中最棒的表演” 说你是在演戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"The performance of a lifetime," and said you were acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.84,0:42:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么看法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.04,0:42:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明那个律师的当事人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Says the lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.88,0:42:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让全世界都相信他有剪刀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the man who convinced the world he had scissors for fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.84,0:42:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（还有没有人看过这部纪录片）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.80,0:42:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（这个人的手指都是剪刀！）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.32,0:42:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想告诉我 那个傻瓜一直在骗我们吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean to tell me that that fool was lying to us the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.72,0:42:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手不是真的用剪刀做的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His hands were not really made of scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.04,0:42:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（2022年8月 弗吉尼亚）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.36,0:42:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（判决后两个月）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.72,0:42:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想细说的是陪审团没看到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What we really wanna get into right now is what the jury didn't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.60,0:42:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场审判的过程中不被允许看的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what wasn't allowed during the course of this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子解封了超过6000份文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Over 6,000 documents have been unsealed in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.52,0:42:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（此事应予解封）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.40,0:42:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这本会对陪审团的决定造成影响的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This would have been very relevant for the jury to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.56,0:42:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要那些文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you wanted to get hold of those documents, 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.08,0:42:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须去弗吉尼亚法院提出请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you had to go to the Virginia courthouse and make a request,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.60,0:43:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普的粉丝众筹了一笔钱 买到了解封的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so JD fans crowdfunded getting hold of the unsealed documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.20,0:43:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（只用超过3300美元 就能解封超过6600页的文件）
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.96,0:43:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.56,0:43:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（欢迎捐款）
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安卓雅・伯克哈特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andrea Burkhart, 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.84,0:43:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YouTube评论员和刑事辩护律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who is a YouTube commentator and is a criminal defense attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.52,0:43:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,众筹资金购买\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she crowdsourced the funds in order to buy these documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.24,0:43:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一直在关注这起案子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you've been watching this case for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.64,0:43:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就会知道安柏・赫德有个习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know that Amber Heard has a habit
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.40,0:43:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会隐瞒无法被证实的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of hiding behind information that can't be verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.32,0:43:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这看起来可能不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it looks like that might not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.40,0:43:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成这一局面的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What spurred this 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.36,0:43:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们在法庭上签署判决书和赔偿时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}was when they were in court to sign the judgment and sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.92,0:43:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹卡瑞特法官表明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Judge Azcarate voiced her intention
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.32,0:43:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她打算解封曾被封存的材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to unseal materials that had previously been sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.68,0:43:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说有很多东西被封存了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she said that many of the things were sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.04,0:43:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们不想让陪审团受到负面影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because we didn't want to have any taint to the jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.88,0:43:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果安柏・赫德 希望让这些东西保密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So if Amber Heard was hoping to keep all of this stuff secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.96,0:43:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为她会发现自己很不走运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think she's gonna find herself out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.92,0:44:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回到飞机事件上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go back to the... there was a plane incident
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.20,0:44:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普据称 在一架飞机上踢了安柏・赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where Depp allegedly kicked Amber Heard on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.64,0:44:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信是在2014年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe it was in 2014.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.36,0:44:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到德普先生 在飞机上脚踢或者互扔东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you observe Mr. Depp kick or throw anything at each other on the plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.88,0:44:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我完全没有这个印象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I don't recall that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.24,0:44:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰尼・德普的助理史蒂芬杜特斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were texts from Johnny Depp's assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.00,0:44:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给安柏・赫德发了短信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stephen Deuters, to Amber Heard, quote...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.84,0:44:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“如果有人对他说实话 告诉他那件事有多糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.48,0:44:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（解封文件 美国审判 2022年）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.12,0:44:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…他会感到震惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.88,0:44:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难过他没有更好的途径
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.92,0:44:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道他昨天的行为有多严重
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.80,0:44:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的不幸在于
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.08,0:44:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完整地记得那件事 所有细节 发生过的一切”
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.92,0:44:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“他非常震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.60,0:44:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我跟他说他踢了你 他哭了”
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.64,0:44:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有公布这些短信？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why was these text messages not introduced?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.20,0:44:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对于安柏・赫德的自证非常关键\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, this felt very pivotal for Amber Heard's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.96,0:44:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭裁定这些证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The court ruled on those that they're irrelevant
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.96,0:44:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与当下的诽谤案无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the... the case at hand of defamation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.00,0:45:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子有太多的证据 现在我们看到了更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, there was so much evidence in this case, and now we're seeing even more of the evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.40,0:45:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在预审听证会上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and... and in the pre-trial hearings, 
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.08,0:45:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们必须决定 哪些证据可以采纳 哪些不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they have to, you know, rule what is admissible, what isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.76,0:45:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一些真的很难界定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, yeah, there's some of these things that are really on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.64,0:45:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底应不应该被采纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of whether they should or shouldn... shouldn't have been admissible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.48,0:45:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普的支持者 很不喜欢德普在周末发布的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Depp supporters have been unliking Depp's victory post
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣告胜利的帖文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.24,0:45:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（最好的还在后面 一个新的篇章已经开始）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.56,0:45:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在法官裁定 与本案无关的审前文件被公开后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The discovery of the unlikes has come after the unsealing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.44,0:45:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们开始不喜欢德普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of pretrial documents that the judge ruled not relevant to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.44,0:45:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天要深入了解这些事 这样你们可以自己判定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're gonna dive into all of these things today so you can decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前被封存的法庭文件 显示德普和他助理往来的短信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Previously sealed court documents, they revealed texts from Depp and his assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.72,0:45:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都在证实赫德的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all but confirming Heard's allegation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指控称他曾在一家私人飞机上 当着员工的面 脚踢和殴打赫德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he'd kicked and beat her in front of his staff on a private plane."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.24,0:45:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（德普粉丝付费三千美元 解封法庭文件 以寻找安柏黑料）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.64,0:45:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（结果找到约翰尼的黑料）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德和史蒂芬杜特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.80,0:45:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在2014年5月24日和25日 之间的任何短信往来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.08,0:46:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然此前拷贝过杜特斯先生的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.32,0:46:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德普先生还是无法定位
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.52,0:46:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在赫德小姐制造出 “波士顿飞机事件”之后
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.60,0:46:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫德和杜特斯之间的一系列短信往来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.56,0:46:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（史蒂芬・杜特斯声称 那些短信被“严重篡改”）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.24,0:46:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（他说自己从未见过 约翰尼对安柏有过肢体暴力）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.08,0:46:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（德普作证称自己 “这辈子”都没有打过女人）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.84,0:46:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是 赫德小姐 拿出的短信的格式
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.88,0:46:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她的其他短信格式都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.96,0:46:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些文本的真实性至关重要 然而受到了严重质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"The veracity of these text messages is critical and subject to serious question."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.04,0:46:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以真相是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.36,0:46:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（妮可拉宾 金钱戒疗中心播客音频）
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.56,0:46:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法回答关于这件事真相的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This question of the truth of the matter I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.24,0:46:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 没人能回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In fact, no one can.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道这两个人之间发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one knows what happened between these two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.24,0:46:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听上去有证据证明 他们相互都有过暴力行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sounds like there is evidence that they were both abusive toward each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很多都是各执一词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's a lot of "he said, she said,"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.20,0:46:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且几乎不可能找到解决办法和真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it's nearly impossible to find resolution and truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.80,0:46:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公众是第二个陪审团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The public is a... a second jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.28,0:47:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己做的决定动摇了舆论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Us making up our own decisions and... really swayed on people's public opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.44,0:47:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括陪审团对他们两个人的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}including the jurors', of these two characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.04,0:47:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被指控做错事的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People who've been accused of wrongdoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.00,0:47:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（茱莉亚・雅各布斯 《纽约时报》播客音频）
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.16,0:47:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…目标是获得某种正义 他们在寻求自己的救赎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the goal is to get a form of justice, a sense of redemption for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.16,0:47:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点在于洗清自己的名声 并试图在舆论法庭上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's about clearing their name and trying to establish
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.08,0:47:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确立这段关系或事件的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what the truth was of this relationship or this incident in a public court of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.12,0:47:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经在舆论法庭上获胜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's won already in the court of opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.32,0:47:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他还需要通过司法程序 洗清自己的名声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he needed the court process to clear his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.60,0:47:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正义的重点其实不是真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The thing is about justice is that it's not about the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.72,0:47:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无关对错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's not about right or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.52,0:47:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是法官或陪审员相信什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's about what the judge or jury believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.36,0:47:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（尼克・维尔 电视嘉宾 维尔档案播客主播）
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们生活在这样的时代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We now live in a time 
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.24,0:47:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不一定相信正义的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where we don't necessarily believe who's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.56,0:47:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信自己最喜欢的人 因为他们的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}...we believe who we like the most because of who they are.
